short_description: A 2004 prison renovation in Megiddo, Israel, uncovered the oldest known Christian worship site, featuring a mosaic with the first public inscription naming Jesus as God. Bear Grylls hosts experts exploring its significance.

movie_name: Imagine Dragons: Live from the Hollywood Bowl
short_description: Live concert film of Imagine Dragons' LOOM Tour finale with LA Film Orchestra. Features hits like "Radioactive" in new arrangements, ending with fireworks. 67,000 fans attended the 4-night residency.
